{"type": "article", "id": 27924, "title": "弹性编织家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-08T07:24:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702161959LzCsybFRio41Z3dD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>我们之前曾经报道过一款由设计工作室 <a href=\"http://layerdesign.com/\">Layer</a> 设计的 <a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/27425.html\">3D 打印轮椅</a> GO，最近他们又为 <a href=\"http://www.moroso.it/?lang=en\">moroso</a> 设计了一套名为 Cradle 的弹性编织家具。采用 3D 可拉伸的织物制成的椅背看上去非常舒适，半包裹的结构带给人一种躺在吊床上的感觉，但又免去了繁琐的爬上爬下的过程。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161956derQjXbDtaiHN46q.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.52322738\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161957CYp2GbwlPOrshzHM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00122249\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161957xbAP2uQ09vUMnmlR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8202934\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161958lBYOah1cxqFRQ8TI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72860636\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}